  "_notes": {
    "purpose": "Per-club colour map for the board's per-lot re-dress (THE HYBRID / Daylight, ruled 8 Jul 2026). Three authored tokens per club; everything else derives in code via lib/club-core.mjs.",
    "tokens": "p = club-primary (shirt), s = club-secondary (trim), t = club-text (legible on primary; white unless primary is light - WOL and MCI are the dark-text exceptions)",
    "derived": "band gradient = p -> darken(p,0.62); photo ground = p -> darken(p,0.45); light-page chip = 12% tint of p; nameplate sub = s (fallback #D9D9D5 when s is white)",
    "keying": "key by FPL team short_name; code = FPL team code (badge filename t{code}). Verify against bootstrap-static at ingest; promoted/renamed clubs get added here. Public-safe: club colours only, no league member data.",
    "status": "starting values from club brand colours; final tuning on the actual TV at the Sprint 4 club-preview pass. Fix clashes HERE, not in code."
  },
